type: software
title: "Resonance: Task-Specialized LLM Orchestration with Minimal Context for Token-Efficient Code Generation"
version: 0.2.3
date-released: 2026-06-12
license: MIT
abstract: >-
  Editor-agnostic framework for specialized LLM bots with deterministic
  minimal-context extraction, achieving 60-85% input token reduction on
  standard Python boilerplate tasks. Includes reproducible benchmarks,
  multi-editor integrations, and open evaluation protocol.
